---
title: "Quantum Providers"
---

<link rel="stylesheet" href="$(root_url)/assets/styles/homepage.css" type="text/css" />

<div id="title" class="banner">
    <h1>Quantum Computing Platforms</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #666; max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto;">
        Explore and connect to leading quantum computing platforms. Select a provider below to access documentation, tools, and resources.
    </p>
</div>

<main style="padding: 40px 20px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin: 30px 0;">
        
        <!-- Provider Card 1: Azure Quantum -->
        <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e6ed; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: all 0.3s ease;" 
             onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)'; this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" 
             onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)'; this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <span style="font-size: 2.5em;">☁️</span>
                <div>
                    <h3 style="margin: 0; color: #2c3e50; font-size: 1.2em;">Microsoft Azure Quantum</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 0.85em; color: #667eea; font-weight: 600;">Core Platforms</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.9em; color: #555; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px;">Quick Links:</label>
                <select style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #e0e6ed; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95em; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s;" 
                        onchange="if(this.value) window.open(this.value, '_blank'); this.selectedIndex=0;" 
                        onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" 
                        onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#e0e6ed'">
                    <option value="">📍 Select a link...</option>
                    <option value="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/quantum/">Platform</option>
                    <option value="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/quantum/">Documentation</option>
                    <option value="https://quantum.microsoft.com/en-us/tools/quantum-katas">Katas</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Provider Card 2: IBM Quantum -->
        <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e6ed; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: all 0.3s ease;" 
             onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)'; this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" 
             onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)'; this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <span style="font-size: 2.5em;">🔬</span>
